reviews_data.review_text: Best camera shop in Charlotte.

So glad I found this place. They're so great. And I really enjoy that they're focused specifically on film and supporting film photography. They've got a nice selection of used cameras that rotates a bit. Film developing, scanning, and printing services are top notch. But most importantly I really enjoy the personal approach that Tony and Cannon have. They'll stop everything and just talk with you about what you're looking to accomplish with photography, from beginner to professional. Did I mention they have a darkroom?! Because they do, and I just spent an afternoon there with my oldest kid having Tony teach them the ropes of film development and print enlargement. And, my favorite part, the gigantic film fridges that aren't stuck behind a counter so you can browse and explore and pick at your leisure.

All in all, Tony and Cannon are great people and supporters of the film photography world who run an excellent shop. I'm happy they're here and wish I had found them sooner!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much!
